<h1>Application Status Update</h1>

<p>Dear <%= @candidate.first_name %>,</p>

<p>
  We wanted to let you know that there has been an update to your application for the
  <strong><%= @job.title %></strong> position at <strong><%= @organization.name %></strong>.
</p>

<h2>Current Status: <%= @application.status.titleize %></h2>

<% case @application.status %>
<% when "screening" %>
  <p>
    Your application is currently being reviewed by our recruiting team. We will be in touch
    if your qualifications match our requirements.
  </p>
<% when "interviewing" %>
  <p>
    Great news! You have been selected to move forward to the interview stage. Our team will
    be reaching out soon to schedule your interview.
  </p>
<% when "assessment" %>
  <p>
    You have advanced to the assessment stage of our hiring process. Please check your email
    for any assessments or tasks that may be assigned.
  </p>
<% when "background_check" %>
  <p>
    You are in the final stages of our hiring process. A background check is currently in progress.
  </p>
<% when "offered" %>
  <p>
    Congratulations! An offer has been extended to you. Please check your email for details
    and next steps.
  </p>
<% when "hired" %>
  <p>
    Welcome to the team! We are excited to have you join <%= @organization.name %>.
    You will receive onboarding information shortly.
  </p>
<% end %>

<p style="margin: 20px 0;">
  <%= link_to "View Full Application Status", @status_url, style: "background-color: #0d6efd; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 4px;" %>
</p>

<p>
  Thank you for your continued interest in <%= @organization.name %>.
</p>

<p>
  Best regards,<br>
  The <%= @organization.name %> Recruiting Team
</p>
